1
00:00:09,118 --> 00:00:09,510
Well, gentlemen,
Well, 先生们,

2
00:00:10,063 --> 00:00:10,850
how can I help you today?
今天我能为你们做些什么?

3
00:00:11,844 --> 00:00:12,843
We're just looking, thanks.
我们只是看看, 谢谢.

4
00:00:13,627 --> 00:00:14,928
Very good, very good.
很好, 很好.

5
00:00:15,622 --> 00:00:16,421
Let me ask you a question.
让我问你一个问题.

6
00:00:17,147 --> 00:00:18,358
Are you interested in glamour?
你是对引人注目的外表(glamour)感兴趣呢?

7
00:00:18,804 --> 00:00:19,123
Or reliability?
还是对可靠性感兴趣?

8
00:00:20,535 --> 00:00:22,296
I'm interested in a car.
我对汽车感兴趣.

9
00:00:22,889 --> 00:00:23,248
Very good.
很好.

10
00:00:24,553 --> 00:00:26,141
What can you tell us about this one?
你能向我们介绍一下这辆车吗?

11
00:00:26,876 --> 00:00:28,775
She's a beauty, isn't she? An 82.
她简直是位美人儿, 是不是? 1982年的.

12
00:00:30,179 --> 00:00:31,104
Was it always this color?
它一直是这个颜色吗?

13
00:00:32,260 --> 00:00:33,187
How many miles on it?
它跑了多少英里了?

14
00:00:34,270 --> 00:00:38,163
162, 000 happy miles. And many more to go, I'm sure.
顺顺当当地跑了16万2千英里. 还可以跑许多英里, 我敢保证.

15
00:00:39,033 --> 00:00:40,213
Was there only one owner?
以前它只有一个车主吗?

16
00:00:40,675 --> 00:00:43,669
Ah, no. Several owners. Several very happy owners.
Ah,no. 有过几个了. 几个十分满意的主人.

17
00:00:44,100 --> 00:00:45,901
How often has it been serviced?
它多长时间维修一次?

18
00:00:46,368 --> 00:00:47,713
You know, the funny thing is,
你知道, 有趣的事情是,

19
00:00:48,166 --> 00:00:50,714
this car ran so well, it hardly ever got serviced.
这车跑得非常好, 它几乎从未维修过.

20
00:00:51,205 --> 00:00:53,011
Except after one or two collisions.
除了一两次撞车后.

21
00:00:53,934 --> 00:00:54,636
Isn't that remarkable?
是不是很棒?

22
00:00:55,613 --> 00:00:56,490
I don't understand.
我不明白.

23
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:59,204
How could the owners ever give it up?
那些车主怎么会不要它了?

24
00:01:00,174 --> 00:01:01,931
Trade-in. They were moving up.
以旧换新嘛. 他们都升级了.

25
00:01:02,587 --> 00:01:05,002
Just like you Kevin. Moving up.
就像你一样, Kevin. 也升级了.

